text: Vilis Cimmermanis (29 December 1896 - 29 May 1936) was a Latvian long-distance runner. He competed at the 1924 Summer Olympics and the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1896 births Category:1936 deaths Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Latvian male long-distance runners Category:Latvian male marathon runners Category:Olympic athletes of Latvia Category:Place of birth missing
